{"tid":1786841,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"福岡黑店 - 天下の燒鳥信秀本店 （屌佢條支那閪）","createTime":"2019-12-17T12:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T04:14:24.000Z","uid":131481,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99d30af34500f05cbe85958ed13c40f5db476bca","tid":1786841,"uid":131481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"話說去左福岡旅行 去左呢間係博多附近既串燒店「天下の燒鳥信秀本店」<br />\n一坐低就問你係咪遊客 叫左我閪口閪面既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那閪</span></strong>黎serve我地<br />\n一俾menu就即刻迫你落order 黑面黑足全程<br />\n想分幾次咁叫黎食但俾佢話我第一次叫得唔夠多<br />\n條<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那閪</span></strong>一serve番日本人就態度180度改變<br />\n老闆同員工啲態度好撚差 又排外連我地之後既韓國人都俾佢地鬧<br />\n仲要埋單先同我地講有table charge 每人俾多400円<br />\n同佢講話唔知道有呢個潛規則就鬧番轉頭話所有人連遊客都知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問佢邊度有寫明 就轉移話題</strong></span><br />\n明明承認餐廳冇提醒過客人有table charge係佢地錯仲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聲大夾惡</strong></span>唔肯扣錢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幾個日本人係度圍住我地用日文屌尻我地 以為我地聽唔明</span></strong><br />\n個光頭呀伯老闆仲要摸我 屌佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咸濕呀伯</span></strong><br />\n條支那閪仲要話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">作為中國人同你地香港台灣人係到嘈 覺得好羞恥</span></strong><br />\n屌佢條偽善支那閪啦 中國人就咪撚去日本做野啦 侵略同屠殺唔撚記得左<br />\n講果句野既時候羞唔羞恥？ 我要俾佢serve先好羞恥呀<br />\n<br />\n呢間支那鋪大家真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好去食</strong></span>，google review好多人都中左伏<br />\n<br />\n利申：我唔識潛規則 但你咁屌尻遊客 仲要請無禮貌支那閪 唔抵幫"},{"pid":"e489a695639fbbee3e034cc18b91549afa52de95","tid":1786841,"uid":37197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"D評語有D比五題有D又一星 好撚兩極"},{"pid":"9ada676b8218f266df9a22b427e2e044cf5de73f","tid":1786841,"uid":129269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"屌我都食過<br />\n個中國人waiter同老細都好撚黑面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次明明入面有好多位<br />\n但係比日本仔入唔比我入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來睇review先知佢地咁唔鍾意遊客"},{"pid":"11825c6152e9d1fe6b8a0b1115b3135c08a2d5de","tid":1786841,"uid":221346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:45:17.000Z","msg":"Review 日本人都好似唔鐘意呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45576d3c0fd18e68bbe356c61dac3f7edf55e24","tid":1786841,"uid":36415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"日本好多居酒屋都會收小菜費或者坐位費，不過態度咁衰就。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7da786131b98a5f3edf97e3caaf20a399c4aa1","tid":1786841,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"有信長唔去去信秀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e59f44a53a4b53c3312904e8b10d76222ba7dc","tid":1786841,"uid":131481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a7da786131b98a5f3edf97e3caaf20a399c4aa1","tid":1786841,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"有信長唔去去信秀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"有早知冇當初<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a59082e7c0aac0212c59c52bcd941379b6d6187","tid":1786841,"uid":343977,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"呢類店有底charge都唔知 第一次去日本？<br />\n架佬會屌泡佬是常識吧？<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇成段野似on9港女發皮四比架佬屌到連支那人都睇佢唔起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}